{"about_the_game":"Dungeon\u2019s Anima is a cooperative Action Roguelite with Bullet Hell mechanics for up to 4 players  (via Online and local co-op).<br><br>\u200bArise as the last undead foot-soldier guarding the Dungeon of your slain master. Imbued with the last of the Dungeon Heart's power, you must collect the souls of your enemies and claim back your dominion after almost facing eradication at the hands of the Human Empire in a dark-fantasy, medieval-steampunk-based world. Bring the fight back to the humans and harvest their soul-power to unlock new abilities, obtain new playable classes and rebuild your fallen kingdom.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618430/extras/About.png?t=1707837852\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A class system based on evolving archetypes.<br></li><li>Unlock up to 15 different playable classes.<br></li><li>A progression system based on collecting adversaries\u2019 souls to upgrade your base, main character, and classes.<br></li><li>A flexible class-building system allows you to rotate between different classes mid-battle.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618430/extras/Mechanics600px.png?t=1707837852\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618430/extras/Class.gif?t=1707837852\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618430/extras/Archer.gif?t=1707837852\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618430/extras/Sorcerer.gif?t=1707837852\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618430/extras/Warrior.gif?t=1707837852\" /><br><br></li><li>A dynamic skill system supporting varied playstyles.<br></li><li>A complex AI system allows for diverse real-time enemy mechanics.<br></li><li>A shared life-pool mechanic for multiplayer sessions.<br></li><li>Local and Online co-op multiplayer experience up to 4-players.<br></li><li>A procedural map system based on challenges and events.<br></li><li>High replay value based on complex upgrade paths, different game endings (on story mode), and different game modes (story new game+, survival, and boss-rush).</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618430/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1707837852","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618430/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1707837852","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618430/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1707837852","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2618430/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1707837852","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"\"Dungeon's Anima\" is a fantasy action game, set against the backdrop of an ethereal army of dark creatures battling the intruding Human Empire.\r\n\r\nFantasy Violence: Players can expect a stylized, cartoony approach to violence that includes scenes of blood and fallen combatants.\r\n\r\nDark Themes: The game delves into elements of dark magic combined with technology, leading to the manifestation of foes that players must confront. You control what is basically an undead skeleton and face modified human forms infused with both fantastical steampunk tech and gruesome details.\r\n\r\nIt's a blend of the arcane and the mechanical, wrapped i